=Description=

"ShareLex is a collaborative program designed to enable communities build and share legal solutions on real legal questions.

ShareLex participants create LaboLex (collaborative R&D workshops) in order to create Q&A on the theme they choose.
Q&A will be published on our website (free software) under creative commons licence.

Sharelex works to facilitate the creation and understanding of the rules governing our societies. 

Disrupting it would result in disrupting the way our society and economy works.

The LaboLex methodology is based on collective intelligence and enable collaboration between law users and law experts, working together as alter ego. Everyone sitting around a table and chatting about law is revolutionary."
(http://imaginationforpeople.org/en/project/sharelex/)

